# =========================
# 1. RUST & CARGO
# =========================
target/
**/*.rs.bk
# Note: Cargo.lock is typically checked in for binary projects to ensure reproducible builds, 
# but target/ MUST be ignored to prevent pushing compiled Rust artifacts.

